Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.15,0:22:40.86,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(75,75)}目指して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.86,0:22:41.52,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(75,75)}夢で！
